{"tid":1082791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跳傘慶祝18歲生日　壽星與教練雙雙墜地身亡","createTime":"2019-03-29T07:43:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T11:55:45.000Z","uid":135638,"like":390,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":105,"replies":[{"pid":"be6c83d5d86218b9eba5f7280149828588647da3","tid":1082791,"uid":135638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:43:27.000Z","msg":"墨西哥一名女子上周日跳傘慶祝18歲生日，但因為降落傘沒有張開，她與教練雙雙從396公（1,300呎）高墜地身亡。<br />\n  <br />\n  卡德納斯（Vanessa Ivonne Melendez Cardenas）在親人陪同下到一個體育會，以跳傘這個特別方式慶生。她與另外4人一同登機跳傘，各人有教練跟隨，但當其他組安全著陸後，卡德納斯卻失蹤。搜救人員獲報到場，在一條公路附近發現她和34歲教練卡斯蒂略（Mauricio Gutierrez Castillo）的屍體。<br />\n<br />\n  體育會負責人蓋坦（Jorge Gaitan）指出，降落傘沒有故障，疑事件是人為造成，指出有人「可能在降落傘無法作反應的高度啟動開傘裝置」，暗示開傘裝置可能在機上已啟動。據當地媒體報導，教練卡斯蒂略經驗豐富，有400次跳傘經驗。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"4885066cd6b81af1e60c299214fe87d6bd340dc3","tid":1082791,"uid":13867,"like":643,"dislike":8,"score":635,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:48:58.000Z","msg":"人為?<br />\n18歲生日當住親人攞命....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fd0659be18b2c208722a6e9936443c2bf36c50","tid":1082791,"uid":162866,"like":68,"dislike":1424,"score":-1356,"citedBy":18,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"1300呎好撚高咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n村屋求其一層都1000呎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850219b1fb84a72a6db48775a3a08b82904344de","tid":1082791,"uid":61625,"like":665,"dislike":8,"score":657,"quote":{"pid":"e8fd0659be18b2c208722a6e9936443c2bf36c50","tid":1082791,"uid":162866,"like":68,"dislike":1424,"score":-1356,"citedBy":18,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T07:51:07.000Z","msg":"1300呎好撚高咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n村屋求其一層都1000呎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T